nd blessings be upon him, about the first mosque placed on the earth. The Prophet said, \u201cIt was the Sacred Mosque.\u201d I asked, \u201cThen which one?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cThe furthest mosque in Jerusalem.\u201d I said, \u201cHow long was between\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24893,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/05\/29\/quds-salat-masjid-aqsa\/","url_meta":{"origin":18460,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Jerusalem: Sins forgiven by praying at Masjid al-Aqsa","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 29, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhen Solomon, son of David, peace and blessings be upon him, built the Sacred House, he asked Allah Almighty for the three things throughout. Solomon asked Allah Almighty for judgment coinciding with His judgment, and\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5635,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/29\/qiblah-al-quds-to-makkah\/","url_meta":{"origin":18460,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Qiblah: Changing direction of prayer from Jerusalem to Mecca","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 29, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, used to pray towards the Sacred House in Jerusalem, then it was revealed to him, \u201cWe have certainly seen you turning your face to the heaven. We will surely turn you to a direction of prayer\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3042,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/04\/24\/pilgrims-makkah-madinah-quds\/","url_meta":{"origin":18460,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Pilgrimage: No religious travel but to Mecca, Medina, Jerusalem","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 24, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cDo not undertake a religious journey but to three mosques: the Sacred Mosque in Mecca, the Mosque of the Messenger of Allah, and the Furthest Mosque in Jerusalem.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1189, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1397 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36133,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/05\/11\/salat-al-quds\/","url_meta":{"origin":18460,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Jerusalem: Virtue of prayers in Masjid al-Aqsa","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 11, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Darda reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe virtue of prayer in Masjid al-Haram is one hundred thousand times better than prayer elsewhere, prayer in this mosque of mine is one thousand times better than prayer elsewhere, and prayer in Bayt al-Maqdis is better than\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":13557,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/04\/13\/tahiyyat-al-masjid\/","url_meta":{"origin":18460,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Nawafil: Greet mosque with Tahiyyatul Masjid prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 13, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Qatadah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhen one of you enters the mosque, let him pray two cycles before he sits down.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 444, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 714 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/18460","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=18460"}],"version-histo